Subject:[child_lit] middle school novels about hunger and emotional hunger
House of Stairs by William Sleator.  Teenagers are kidnapped and put in a house filled with stairways, where food is provided by a mechanical device (can't remember exactly what sort).  As time goes by, less and less food is provided.
